data.description: Welcome home to this adorable 1900's farmhouse in the heart of Altoona. This property is on .38 of an acre and is a corner lot! Perfect for someone looking for an opportunity to stay in town while owning a good sized piece of property. Updated appliances throughout the kitchen make for a great space for cooking! The open living area into the dining room is perfect for a cozy night in. The bedroom upstairs features two closets and makes a good space for the 2nd bedroom. Outback features a privacy fenced in yard and a 24x30 2 car garage that was built in 2016! Close to schools, restaurants, shopping, and the dog park. Schedule a showing today!
